    "body": "- **tilelang frontend v2**\r\n\n\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **New Features**\n  * AST-based DSL transformation and compilation for Python-defined kernels\n  * Expanded dtype system with broad scalar/vector aliases and conversions\n  * v2 Builder and macros/prim_func decorators with richer IR-generation workflows\n  * Generic-typed JIT with parallel compilation and improved autotuning APIs\n  * Runtime utilities for safe compilation/inspection and improved progress display selection\n\n* **Tests**\n  * New tests covering language frontend v2, dtypes, macros, JIT par-compile and par-compiled kernels\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
